d":3801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T21:47:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/09.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84d472bcf2e0a7930cc2f6fccec607fa06bdd320","tid":2361343,"uid":49392,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T21:53:30.000Z","msg":"&quot;拜登：中國須按「國際規範」行事 並盼川普參加自己的就職典禮 - 國際 - 中時新聞網&quot; <a href=\"https://www-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20201204005570-260408?amp_gsa=1&amp;amp_js_v=a6&amp;usqp=mq331AQHKAFQArABIA%3D%3D#amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%20%251%24s&amp;aoh=16103154005776&amp;csi=1&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;ampshare=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201204005570-260408\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fv%2Fs%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Famp%2Frealtimenews%2F20201204005570-260408%3Famp_gsa%3D1%26amp_js_v%3Da6%26usqp%3Dmq331AQHKAFQArABIA%253D%253D%23amp_tf%3D%25E4%25BE%2586%25E8%2587%25AA%2520%25251%2524s%26aoh%3D16103154005776%26csi%3D1%26referrer%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.google.com%26ampshare%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.chinatimes.com%252Frealtimenews%252F20201204005570-260408&d=7oH93WZedTbABA3XB48d7fsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=9168cc44\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www-chinatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org/v/s/www.chinatimes.com/amp/realtimenews/20201204005570-260408?amp_gsa=1&amp;amp_js_v=a6&amp;usqp=mq331AQHKAFQArABIA%3D%3D#amp_tf=%E4%BE%86%E8%87%AA%20%251%24s&amp;aoh=16103154005776&amp;csi=1&amp;referrer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com&amp;ampshare=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Frealtimenews%2F20201204005570-260408</a><br />\n<br />\n中時新聞係台灣藍營，內容引述CNN訪問<br />\n<br />\n美國總統當選人拜登3日接受有線電視新聞網（CNN）專訪。談到中國議題時，拜登表示，中國必須按照「國際規範」行事，他也會堅持要求對方停止盜竊美方國家機密及「人工智慧（AI）能力」的行為。他還說，支持採循多邊方法，將聯合美國在歐洲和亞太地區的盟友，與伊朗、俄羅斯及中國等國家打交道。<br />\n<br />\n在訪談中，拜登被問到，中國是否應為在疫情爆發初期處理不當及隱匿資訊「受懲罰」？拜登答說，他的目標將是「向中國表明，若你們願意按照國際規則行事，我們也會依此與你們打交道。若你們不願意，我們也就不會這麼做。」<br />\n<br />\n拜登說：「關鍵並不在於要為新冠疫情懲罰他們，而是堅持他們須遵循現有的國際規範。」他還談到，他會堅持要求（中方）停止盜竊（美方）國家機密及「人工智慧能力」。他又說，中外合資經營企業，規定中方占股不低於51％，這「是我們政府不能夠接受的」。<br />\n<br />\n談到外交政策，拜登也指出，「我們應當成為大集團的一部分，以便與伊朗、俄羅斯及中國等國家打交道。」他宣布說，「我現在還不能定政策，但希望恢復與歐洲和太平洋-印度洋地區親密的盟友關係。」拜登坦承，「與歐盟的會談將很艱難，我在這方面沒有幻想。」<br />\n<br />\n此外，拜登特別提到，希望現任總統川普能夠參加自己的就職典禮，作為美國權力和平交接的象徵，向全世界發出穩定且有力的訊息。<br />\n<br />\n拜登此前在接受《紐約時報》專欄作家佛里曼（Thomas Friedman）電話專訪時表示，他就任後不會立即撤銷川普總統對中國加徵的25％關稅，並將與盟友共同制衡中國。拜登稱，與中國打交道，最重要的就是「制衡」，而獲取更多制衡優勢的部分辦法，就是由政府主導對研發、基礎設施和教育進行大規模投資，以便更好地與中國競爭。"},{"pid":"a9448b8f61be2e1303f897828b871706d0cec79d","tid":2361343,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"126aef253977dd09c789208d86bcdd3d850f6fe5","tid":2361343,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"聯合報出名9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"藍到黑，差唔到係中國時報咁"},{"pid":"38db0c07f567d36a5ea7b399456c7b1069743233","tid":2361343,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T23:15:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"849674852edc9a7a42712c51e56a6d5ed726a2d9","tid":2361343,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9448b8f61be2e1303f897828b871706d0cec79d","tid":2361343,"uid":51271,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"126aef253977dd09c789208d86bcdd3d850f6fe5","tid":2361343,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T14:47:16.000Z","msg":"聯合報出名9up <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-10T23:12:48.000Z","msg":"藍到黑，差唔到係中國時報咁"},"citedBy":